f=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feMorphology\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feOffset\"><code>&lt;feOffset&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/fePointLight\"><code>&lt;fePointLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpotLight\"><code>&lt;feSpotLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTile\"><code>&lt;feTile&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face\"><code>&lt;font-face&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-format\"><code>&lt;font-face-format&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-name\"><code>&lt;font-face-name&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-src\"><code>&lt;font-face-src&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-uri\"><code>&lt;font-face-uri&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>G\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/g\"><code>&lt;g&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>H\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/hkern\"><code>&lt;hkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>I\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>J-L\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/linearGradient\"><code>&lt;linearGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>M\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/metadata\"><code>&lt;metadata&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section>\n<p>The <strong><code>path</code></strong> attribute has two different meanings, either it defines a text path along which the characters of a text are rendered, or a motion path along which a referenced element is animated.</p>\n<p>You can use this attribute with the following SVG elements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateMotion\"><code>&lt;animateMotion&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">html,\nbody,\nsvg</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 100 100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>MyPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>none<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>silver<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M10,90 Q90,90 90,45 Q90,10 50,10 Q10,10 10,40 Q10,70 45,70 Q70,70 75,50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>textPath</span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">path</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M10,90 Q90,90 90,45 Q90,10 50,10 Q10,10 10,40 Q10,70 45,70 Q70,70 75,50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      Quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>textPath</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"420\" height=\"220\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/path/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"animatemotion","title":"animateMotion","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateMotion\"><code>&lt;animateMotion&gt;</code></a>, <code>path</code> defines the motion path, expressed in the same format and interpreted the same way as the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/d\">d</a></code> geometric property for the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a> element. The effect of a motion path animation is a translation along the x- and y-axes of the current user coordinate system by the x and y values computed over time.</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n      <td><code>&lt;path-data&gt;</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n      <td><em>None</em></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"path-data\"><code>&lt;path-data&gt;</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>This value defines the motion path along which the referenced element is animated. For detailed information about the commands that can be used, see the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/d#path_commands\">explanation for the <code>d</code> attribute</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"textpath","title":"textPath","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a>, <code>path</code> defines the path onto which the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Glyph\">glyphs</a> of a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a> element will be rendered. An empty string indicates that there is no path data for the element. This means that the text within the <code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code> element does not render or contribute to the bounding box of the <code>&lt;text&gt;</code> element. If the attribute is not specified, the path specified in <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/href\">href</a></code> is used instead.</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n      <td><code>&lt;path-data&gt;</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n      <td><em>Path specified in <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/href\">href</a></code></em></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"path-data_2\"><code>&lt;path-data&gt;</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>This value defines the text path along which the glyphs of the <code>&lt;text&gt;</code> element are aligned. For detailed information about the commands that can be used, see the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/d#path_commands\">explanation for the <code>d</code> attribute</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/text.html#TextPathElementPathAttribute","title":"Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/specs/animations/#AnimateMotionElementPathAttribute","title":"SVG Animations Level 2"}],"query":"undefined"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"animateMotion","id":"animatemotion"},{"text":"textPath","id":"textpath"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"}],"summary":"The path attribute has two different meanings, either it defines a text path along which the characters of a text are rendered, or a motion path along which a referenced element is animated.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-09-14T09:21:13.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"path","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/svg/attribute/path","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/svg/attribute/path/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f42cbd9709e5c61e3d4833f6d911aae9bed5275d","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG Attribute reference"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/path","title":"path"}],"pageTitle":"path - SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics | MDN","noIndexing":false}}